channel.title: Myspace phishers
channel.description:
I had an announcement on my MySpace page that my account had been phished, so I had to change my password in order to unblock my account. However, everytime I access the page, it still tells me that I am blocked and can't do anything. So I ran a full system scan on my laptop and it found a tracking cookie and this thing called "Hacktool", which is supposedly used for game cheats. When I tried to delete it though, no delete options came up.
My sister thinks I have fucked up my laptop, yet she ws the one downloading off LimeWire earlier yesterday, and all this stuff started happening about 4 hours after she had downloaded over 70 songs.
Suggestions?
